<s> My thinking is that if the folks before us couldn't give us enforcable definition of resource... then we're going to have difficulty defining an enforcable defintion of "same resource".  </s>
<s> Therefore we can talk about "same resource", but we shouldn't really try to *strictly* define it.  </s>
